item.title: CVE-2022-4580|2024-08-03T01:41:45.676Z -- unknown -- twenty20%20image%20before-after
item.description: The Twenty20 Image Before-After WordPress plugin through 1.5.9 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
